			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Go to dranik's scar. Run north up to the east side of the wall, back up and you can see the Kyv patrolling across the top. Watch pathing patterns. At the correct time malosini one of them and it will warp over to you. just b4 the malosini hits, /pet attack. The pet will intercept the Kyv and he wont even touch you.  If you get two just hoe or burn them down unless you have a good pet focus or some aa's. Rince repeat a few thousand times. Faction to ally goes very very fast this way as Dranik's Scar mobs have the lowest hp. 
<br />

<br />
Note: Do not kill any of the Dragorns in DS. They will ruin your loyalists faction. Ukuns, Kyv, Nocs are great to kill in any zone. BTW...The Dragorns in Nobles Causeway are fine to kill as well. Need <span style="font-weight: bold">warmly</span> to get OoW silk armor tier #1 quests, Need <span style="font-weight: bold">ally</span> to get OoW silk armor tier #2.<br />_________________<br /><img src="http://members.cox.net/dtresendes/danisig.png" border="0" />
<br />
<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=639739" target="_blank" class="postlink">Danille Impholder</a>
<br />
Ayonae Ro ~ Vallis Aspectus
<br />
Keep Norrath Safe</span><span class="gensmall"><br /><br />Last edited by danille on Tue Nov 23, 2004 5:17 pm; edited 2 times in total</span></td>
